# Authentication

- All endpoints require authentication unless explicitly marked public
- Public endpoints: `/health`, `/version`, `/auth/login`, `/auth/refresh`
- Use `get_current_user` dependency for protected routes
- Use `require_role()` for role-based access control
- Never hardcode secrets — use environment variables via pydantic-settings
